title: Create FAQ and Docs on Gitbook
body:
Discord has been the only place to find information about screensaver.world, but many people do not have access to or are not willing to join the server. As we progress, it would be helpful to create an FAQ and Docs explaining the project on Gitbook with the URL docs.screensaver.world - some examples are:
https://docs.sushi.com/
https://docs.cargo.build/
author: 0xe288a00DF4b697606078876788e4D64633CD2e01
